/*******************************************************************************/
/
/ These are the examples of ABACUS program.
/
/*******************************************************************************/

These examples show how to output the H/S matrix.
For the H/S matrix in K-space:
	- set 'out_mat_hs' to '1'
After finishing the job, the H (S) matrix files are outputed in OUT.${suffix}
More information can be found here:
https://abacus.deepmodeling.com/en/latest/advanced/elec_properties/hs_matrix.html#out-mat-hs

While, for printing H(R)/S(R) matrices in real space:
	- set 'out_mat_hs2' to '1'
After finishing the job, the H (S) matrix files are outputed in OUT.${suffix}
More information can be found here:
https://abacus.deepmodeling.com/en/latest/advanced/elec_properties/hs_matrix.html#out-mat-hs2

Besides, one can directly output the S matrix without SCF calculation by:
	- set 'calculation' to 'get_s'
	- set 'out_mat_hs' or 'out_mat_hs2' to '1'

